<!--프랑스_레지옹_정보-->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = AdministrativeRegion
| mappings =
	{{ConstantMapping | ontologyProperty = country | value = France }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 이름 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 원래이름 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 아롱디스망 | ontologyProperty = arrondissement }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 칸톤 | ontologyProperty = canton }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 코뮌 | ontologyProperty = commune }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 데파르트망 | ontologyProperty = department }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 인구밀도 | ontologyProperty = populationDensity | unit = inhabitantsPerSquareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 넓이 | ontologyProperty = areaTotal | unit = squareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 조사인구 | ontologyProperty = populationTotal }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 예측인구 | ontologyProperty = populationTotal }}
end}}
